							<h3>WE HAVE MOVED</h3>
							<p>
								The BCA website has been revamped to serve you better. <br />
                                This link may have been moved permanently to a new address.<br />
                            <br />
                             You will be redirected to the <a href="https://www1.bca.gov.sg"> BCA home page  </a>in <span id="counter"+>10</span> seconds.

                                <br />   Visit the <a href="https://www1.bca.gov.sg">revamped BCA website here.</a>
                             </p>




                                <script>

                                     setInterval(function () {
                                         var div = document.querySelector("#counter");

                                         var count = div.textContent * 1 - 1;
                                         div.textContent = count;
                                         if (count <= 0) {

                                             window.location.href = 'https://www1.bca.gov.sg';
                                         }
                                     }, 1000);

                                </script>






